* 1st Lt. [[Donald Gott]]<ref name="Valor at its Highest">{{cite journal | last =Frisbee | first =John L. | title =Valor:"Valor at its Highest" | journal =Air Force Magazine  | volume =72 | issue =6 | pages = | publisher = | date =June 1989 | url= http://www.afa.org/magazine/valor/0689valor.asp | id = | accessdate =2007-01-09  }}</ref>
