* 2nd Lt. [[Joseph Sarnoski]] (awarded posthumously).<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.homeofheroes.com/moh/citations_1940_wwii/sarnoski.html|title=MOH citation of SARNOSKI, JOSEPH R. |accessdate= 2007-01-12}}</ref>
* Sgt. [[Maynard Harrison Smith| Maynard H. Smith]] <U+2014> The first enlisted airman ever to win the nation's highest decoration.<ref>{{cite journal | last =Frisbee | first =John L. | title =Valor:First of the Few | journal =Air Force Magazine  | volume =67 | issue =4 | pages = | publisher = | date= April 1984 | url= http://www.afa.org/magazine/valor/0484valor.asp | id = | accessdate =2007-01-09  }}</ref>
